         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Polemon, Epistates of Kerkeosiris, from Tapentos daughter of Horos, of the same village. An attack was made upon my dwelling by Arsinoe and her son Phatres, who went off with the contract relating to my house and other business documents. Therefore since I am seriously ill, being in want of the necessaries of life and bodily ï¿½ (Here the papyrus breaks off).</ab>
